[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3289] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3292] 2
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3300] 3
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3301] 4
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3306] 5
Now 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3314] appends to the history instead of replacing it
API improvements to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3309] allow embedded nushell to have custom commands
Internal implementation 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3310] improvements to 
``which``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3312] to 
``all``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3315] to 
``math``
 commands
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3320] to 
``to``
 and 
``from``
 commands
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3325] to 
``compact``
Updated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3322] ``echo ..``
 to no longer prints integers
Removed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3311] help flags from the 
``$scope.commands``
 display
Removed the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3308] dupes in get_commands/get_command_names
Fixes to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3305] viewing Value as a filepath
Move 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3294] arg deserialization out of 
``str``
Cleaned up 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3297] error handling
Fixes to how 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3303] rest arguments are handled
Fixes to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3293] ``ansi rgb fg``
Updated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3291] the default prompt
Autoview and table now 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3287] read from the in-memory config
Do not 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3286] store whitespace entries in the history
Simplified 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3283] internal handling of the runnable context
Fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3280] external output busy-waiting
Remove 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3278] ``rm``
's trash flag if it's not supported
Fixed a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3271] panic when timestamp is out of range
Sysinfo dependency has been 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3267] updated
Config commands 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3265] are now more unified internally
Added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3257] TiB and PiB units
Improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3249] auto-suggestion for aliases and custom commands
More 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3247] logging and tests
Now 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3243] parses decimal units
Use 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3242] one main function to run scripts
Fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3235] errors when deleting a FIFO
Fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3234] capitalizations of Unicode
Fixes to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3335] path sync'ing
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3336] more path fixes
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3339] improvements to dynamic blocks
